reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect size, looks great
reviews.reviewText: This fit in well with our bathrooms remodel, a spa theme. We placed it over the tub on (an otherwise bare wall) & worked perfect bringing the look together.We did not use the sticky hook it came with, those arnt any good. Used a small white screw in hook, into the drywall, so no worries of it falling. Should last well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I have a very mentally draining job this wreath is so rejuvenating and calming plus it adds much needed decor to such a blank space! I opted to place outside the shower and the affect (effect?) is still calming. I love that every piece of this is natural

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Do not buy for fragrance but it is a lovely decor piece
reviews.reviewText: This is very pretty and could go in any room. The dried eucalyptus and lavender is hands down better quality than the fake versions I’ve seen. The smell is nice at unboxing but it does not last long. I ended up using mine in the kitchen instead of the bathroom as planned. The sticky hook it came with fell off the wall within minutes so I used a clear thumb tack and wrapped some of the twine around it so it’s not even noticeable. I would recommend unboxing outside or over some craft or newspaper as it is messy with mostly loose lavender. I ended up putting that in a tiny decorative spice bowl and placing on my bathroom counter. Overall I love this piece and do not regret purchasing despite lack of fragrance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: If you want a fuller look, buy 2. Smells wonderful! But the smell only lasted about a week. Haven't had an issue with bleeding except once when I actually got them wet wet. No issues bleeding dyes with just steam. Adds a touch of relaxation to your bathroom. Seeds will drop if you hit it and I only lost a petal off the roses. I'd definitely buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Does not have any smell even when wet
reviews.reviewText: I ordered 3 of these for Christmas gifts. They came crushed and did not have any smell. The bundles were just dried flowers. Not worth the money and an embarrassing gift.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Almost got it right 😁
reviews.reviewText: Package & Delivery were spot on. Pulled it out and was easy to hang (i used a decorative tac) I hung in bathroom near toilet (didn't want it to get wet. Smell is diminishing but still there. I have a Eucalyptus essential oil I can mist if I need to adjust the scent. I would've rather NOT have the lettered beads at all, than to have them miss-spelled though.I'm assuming it was supposed to say HOME? 🙄 I bought 2 (1 as a gift) hope that one isn't spelled wrong)*It's pretty and smells nice .

reviews.reviewText: Great product, is not painted like some other brands and very aromatic. I was concerned buying them online but the quality is excellent.
